I agree very much with Prav. Khasirath does not believe that the Innoruuk found and fought in the Plane of Hate is the true Innoruuk. In fact, the 'Plane of Hate' is only a pocket of the true realm. A pocket designed and made open to powerful adventurers by Innoruuk Himself. This is His test! Only those strong enough in Hate (willingly and knowingly or not) can fight His Avatar and complete His test. For proof, look at the items and quests involved. He wants His Chosen to have the best equipment to fight His wars, so He provides them as loot upon killing His Avatar... His test.<br>
<br>
So I say Raids are more then all right, they are our duty as His Chosen. We must prove our place by facing and defeating His test! <br>
